        <unitName xml:lang="en">kg</unitName>
        <comment xml:lang="en">Calculated value. Some of the bamboo residues which are produced as a by-product are used as internal fuel for the required heat input for the drying process. Emissions for the combustion of bamboo residues are approximated with the combustion of wood chips using the dataset “heat production, softwood chips from forest, at furnace 300kW”. It is assumed that per kg of bamboo pole, 0.066 kg of waste bamboo residues [kg of dry mass] are burned as fuel.</comment>
